910
01:26:32,886 --> 01:26:36,390
NO.  NO.
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

911
01:26:36,390 --> 01:26:38,392
WE'VE GOTTA
CALL THE POLICE.
I'LL GO TO JAIL.

912
01:26:38,392 --> 01:26:40,894
RUINED.
SCANDAL.

913
01:26:41,395 --> 01:26:44,398
I'M A MURDERER.
I'M A GODDAMN MURDERER !

914
01:26:44,898 --> 01:26:47,901
LOOK, WE'RE ALL
IN THIS TOGETHER.
LET'S CALL THE POLICE.

915
01:26:47,901 --> 01:26:49,903
NO.  NO !

916
01:26:51,905 --> 01:26:54,908
NO, WE'VE GOT
TO HIDE THE BODY.

917
01:26:55,409 --> 01:26:57,911
HIDE IT WHERE IT
WILL NEVER BE FOUND.

918
01:27:34,414 --> 01:27:38,418
OH, JESUS.
[ Sobbing ]

919
01:27:39,419 --> 01:27:41,922
SHUT UP !

920
01:27:50,931 --> 01:27:54,434
- [ Ricky ]
DO WE REALLY HAVE TO ?
- [ Sears ]  WE HAVE NO CHOICE.

921
01:27:54,434 --> 01:27:57,437
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU'RE DOIN',
NED ?
YES !

922
01:28:30,971 --> 01:28:33,974
- OH, JESUS !
- SHE MOVED !

923
01:28:33,974 --> 01:28:36,977
- OH, MY GOD.
- SHE'S DEAD.

924
01:28:36,977 --> 01:28:38,979
I TELL YOU, SHE'S DEAD.

925
01:28:48,989 --> 01:28:52,492
NO !  EVA !  EVA !

926
01:28:52,492 --> 01:28:55,996
NO !  EVA !  EVA !
NO !

927
01:28:57,998 --> 01:29:00,000
EVA.  EVA.

928
01:29:04,504 --> 01:29:07,507
[ Coughing ]
EVA.

929
01:29:07,507 --> 01:29:10,510
[ Sobbing ]

930
01:29:13,513 --> 01:29:16,516
[ Sobbing Continues ]

931
01:29:39,539 --> 01:29:42,542
[ Panting ]

932
01:29:49,549 --> 01:29:53,553
WE'D NEVER TALK ABOUT IT AGAIN.
[ Ricky ]
NOT EVEN WITH EACH OTHER.

933
01:29:53,553 --> 01:29:56,056
WE TOLD OURSELVES
IT WAS A TRICK OF THE LIGHT.

934
01:29:56,056 --> 01:30:00,560
WE PUT IT BEHIND US.
BACK TO WORK, SCHOOL.

935
01:30:00,560 --> 01:30:02,562
GOT ON WITH THE REST
OF OUR LIVES.

936
01:30:03,063 --> 01:30:04,564
WASN'T SHE MISSED ?

937
01:30:05,065 --> 01:30:09,069
THE TOWN ASSUMED SHE'D GOT
TIRED OF IT AND MOVED ON.

938
01:30:09,569 --> 01:30:11,571
THERE WAS A BIT OF TALK,
BUT IT DIED DOWN.

939
01:30:12,072 --> 01:30:14,074
YOU COULD ALMOST FEEL
THE SIGH OF RELIEF
THAT SHE HAD GONE.

940
01:30:14,074 --> 01:30:16,576
YOU MEAN NOBODY EVER
SHOWED UP ASKIN' ABOUT HER ?

941
01:30:16,576 --> 01:30:19,579
IT WAS AS IF SHE
HAD NEVER BEEN HERE.

942
01:30:19,579 --> 01:30:22,082
AS IF IT HAD
NEVER HAPPENED.

943
01:30:22,082 --> 01:30:25,085
AS IF WE HAD DREAMED
THE WHOLE AFFAIR.

944
01:30:25,085 --> 01:30:27,587
AH, WHAT ABOUT THE CAR ?

945
01:30:28,088 --> 01:30:30,590
STILL AT THE BOTTOM
OF THE DEDHAM POND.

946
01:30:32,592 --> 01:30:35,095
AND YOU STAYED HERE ?
YOU NEVER LEFT.

947
01:30:35,095 --> 01:30:38,098
WE COULDN'T.
NOT FOR LONG, ANYWAY.

948
01:30:38,098 --> 01:30:42,102
WHAT ELSE COULD WE HAVE DONE ?
RUINED FOUR MORE LIVES ?

949
01:30:42,602 --> 01:30:45,605
COULD HAVE GONE TO THE POLICE
AND TAKEN OUR CHANCES.

950
01:30:45,605 --> 01:30:49,109
INSTEAD, WE DID THIS...
OBSCENE THING.

951
01:30:53,613 --> 01:30:57,117
YOU THINK IT'S EVA ?

952
01:30:57,617 --> 01:31:01,621
- AND THAT SOMEHOW OR OTHER
SHE'S COME BACK TO US, HUH ?
- YEAH.

953
01:31:02,622 --> 01:31:04,624
SO DO I.

954
01:31:04,624 --> 01:31:09,129
I THINK MAYBE BY GROWIN' OLD,

955
01:31:09,129 --> 01:31:13,133
MAYBE THE FORCES, OR WHATEVER
THE HELL YOU WANT TO CALL THEM,
HAVE INCREASED.

956
01:31:13,133 --> 01:31:15,635
AND THESE STORIES
AND THESE NIGHTMARES--

957
01:31:15,635 --> 01:31:19,639
- MAYBE THE GUILT--
- IS THAT WHAT KILLED EDWARD ?

958
01:31:19,639 --> 01:31:22,642
AND MY BROTHER.
AND DR. JAFFREY.

959
01:31:23,143 --> 01:31:24,644
[ Sighs ]

960
01:31:25,145 --> 01:31:28,648
I THINK GREGORY BATE
AND THE BOY...
ARE HELPIN' HER.

961
01:31:28,648 --> 01:31:31,651
I WANT TO GO TO HER HOUSE.

962
01:31:31,651 --> 01:31:34,654
I HOPE YOU'LL COME WITH ME.

963
01:31:37,157 --> 01:31:39,659
I WILL.

964
01:32:00,680 --> 01:32:04,684
AND WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING ?
OUT.

965
01:32:04,684 --> 01:32:07,187
AH.  YOU'LL DO
NO SUCH THING.

966
01:32:07,187 --> 01:32:11,191
YOU'LL MARCH RIGHT BACK
UPSTAIRS BEFORE YOU
CATCH PNEUMONIA.

967
01:32:11,191 --> 01:32:13,693
- BUT I HAVE TO GO OUT.
- WHERE ?

968
01:32:17,697 --> 01:32:21,201
YOU INFURIATE ME
WITH YOUR SECRETS.

969
01:32:21,201 --> 01:32:25,205
I'VE BEEN MARRIED TO YOU
FOR 32 YEARS,

970
01:32:25,205 --> 01:32:29,709
AND I'M NO CLOSER TO YOU
THAN THE DAY WE WERE MARRIED.

971
01:32:30,210 --> 01:32:32,212
I'LL TELL YOU IN THE SPRING.

972
01:32:32,212 --> 01:32:34,214
I'M GOING TO TAKE YOU
TO THE SOUTH OF FRANCE,

973
01:32:34,214 --> 01:32:38,218
TO ANTIBES, SAINT-TROPEZ,
ANYWHERE YOU WANT TO GO.

974
01:32:38,218 --> 01:32:41,721
AND I'M GONNA TELL YOU
THE STORY OF MY LIFE.

975
01:33:07,414 --> 01:33:10,917
[ Door Opening ]

976
01:33:15,422 --> 01:33:18,425
I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D SET FOOT
IN THIS HOUSE AGAIN.

977
01:33:18,925 --> 01:33:21,428
IF ONLY WE'D BEEN 30
INSTEAD OF 20.

978
01:33:21,428 --> 01:33:24,431
OH, WHAT FOOLS
WE WERE.

979
01:33:24,431 --> 01:33:26,433
I DON'T THINK
ANYBODY'S HERE.

980
01:33:26,433 --> 01:33:29,936
SHE'S HERE.
I'M SURE OF IT.

981
01:33:31,938 --> 01:33:33,940
YOU WANT TO TRY
UPSTAIRS ?

982
01:33:36,943 --> 01:33:40,447
NOTHING WILL COME OF THIS.

983
01:33:41,948 --> 01:33:43,950
DO YOU WANT TO STAY
DOWNSTAIRS, MR. JAMES ?

984
01:33:46,953 --> 01:33:49,456
NOT ON YOUR LIFE.

985
01:33:49,456 --> 01:33:52,959
[ Ricky ]
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE, BUT
ALL THIS WAS SO BEAUTIFUL THEN.

986
01:33:52,959 --> 01:33:56,963
THE ROOMS DOWNSTAIRS AND HER
ROOM UP HERE, JUST BEAUTIFUL.

987
01:33:58,465 --> 01:34:01,968
SO WAS ALMA'S.
OHH !

988
01:34:03,470 --> 01:34:05,972
AAAH.

989
01:34:13,980 --> 01:34:17,484
[ Groans ]
ALL RIGHT, THAT'S ENOUGH.

990
01:34:17,484 --> 01:34:20,987
WE'LL ALL GO.
HE CAN'T BE MOVED.

991
01:34:20,987 --> 01:34:24,491
PLEASE, SEARS.
IF WE STAY TOGETHER--
RICKY, DON'T ARGUE WITH ME !

992
01:34:24,491 --> 01:34:28,995
I'M TOO OLD, TOO TIRED
AND TOO FRIGHTENED.

993
01:34:28,995 --> 01:34:33,500
SEARS !
I'LL BE BACK WITH HELP
AS SOON AS I CAN.

994
01:34:38,004 --> 01:34:40,507
I COULD NEVER MAKE HIM
DO ANYTHING HE DIDN'T
WANT TO DO.

995
01:34:59,025 --> 01:35:02,028
- YOU OKAY ?
- YEAH.

996
01:35:13,039 --> 01:35:15,041
ALL CLEAR SO FAR.

997
01:35:18,545 --> 01:35:21,047
CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
YEAH.

998
01:35:47,574 --> 01:35:50,076
[ Woman Snickering ]

999
01:35:51,578 --> 01:35:53,580
RICKY ?

1000
01:35:55,582 --> 01:35:57,584
[ Louder ]
RICKY ?

1001
01:36:06,593 --> 01:36:08,595
FIND ANYTHING ?

1002
01:36:09,596 --> 01:36:12,098
JUST AN EMPTY ROOM.

1003
01:36:12,098 --> 01:36:15,602
YOU OKAY ?
YEAH.

1004
01:36:15,602 --> 01:36:18,605
I WAS JUST THINKING.
WHAT, ABOUT
THE SIDEWALKS AGAIN ?

1005
01:36:18,605 --> 01:36:21,107
NO, YOU SCAMP.

1006
01:36:21,107 --> 01:36:25,612
IT'S SEARS.
I'M WORRIED ABOUT HIM.

1007
01:36:25,612 --> 01:36:30,617
A LOT OF PEOPLE THINK I TAKE
TOO MUCH GUFF FROM HIM,
BUT I DON'T MIND THAT.

1008
01:36:30,617 --> 01:36:35,121
IT'S SORT OF PERMANENT
JUNIOR PARTNERSHIP STUFF,
YOU KNOW ?

1009
01:36:35,622 --> 01:36:40,627
WHAT CAN I DO ?  I'VE BEEN
MARRIED TO THE GUY AS SURE
AS I'VE BEEN MARRIED TO STELLA.

1010
01:36:43,129 --> 01:36:45,632
HE'LL BE OKAY.

1011
01:36:45,632 --> 01:36:47,634
I WONDER.

1012
01:37:16,246 --> 01:37:19,749
[ Screams ]

1013
01:37:39,769 --> 01:37:42,722
[ Moans ]

1014
01:37:52,732 --> 01:37:55,235
DANCE WITH ME,
YOU LITTLE TOAD.

1015
01:37:56,736 --> 01:37:59,739
- [ Fenny Snarls ]
- [ Horn Honking ]

1016
01:38:04,244 --> 01:38:07,247
[ Wind Howling ]

1017
01:38:14,254 --> 01:38:16,256
MAYBE HE JUST GOT STUCK
IN THE SNOW.

1018
01:38:16,256 --> 01:38:19,759
HE'D HAVE COME BACK
IF HE WAS ALL RIGHT.

1019
01:38:20,760 --> 01:38:22,762
I DON'T LIKE IT.

1020
01:38:29,269 --> 01:38:33,273
WE'LL END IT, RICKY.
WE'LL LAY HER TO REST.

1021
01:38:33,273 --> 01:38:36,776
- AN OLD MAN AND A PUP, HUH ?
- WE ARE THE CHOWDER SOCIETY
NOW.

1022
01:38:38,278 --> 01:38:40,780
[ Groans ]

1023
01:38:42,282 --> 01:38:46,786
SEARS WAS RIGHT.
YOU SOUND LIKE KNUTE ROCKNE.

1024
01:38:46,786 --> 01:38:49,289
[ Chuckles ]
HERE.

1025
01:38:49,289 --> 01:38:51,791
I HAVE TO GET YOU
TO A DOCTOR.

1026
01:38:57,297 --> 01:38:59,299
BE RIGHT BACK.

1027
01:39:34,334 --> 01:39:37,837
- THANK GOODNESS
YOU CAME ALONG.
- LUCKY FOR BOTH OF US, RICKY.

1028
01:39:40,340 --> 01:39:42,842
[ Engine Revs, Tires Squeal ]

1029
01:39:47,847 --> 01:39:52,352
DON'T STRUGGLE,
OR I'LL KILL YOU RIGHT NOW !
YOU HEAR ME ?

1030
01:39:52,852 --> 01:39:55,355
- YOU'LL BE QUIET ?
- YEAH.

1031
01:39:55,355 --> 01:39:59,359
- THAT'S A GOOD LITTLE RABBIT.
- WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS ?

1032
01:40:01,361 --> 01:40:03,863
WOULD YOU LIKE TO
LIVE FOREVER, RICKY ?

1033
01:40:03,863 --> 01:40:07,367
[ Laughs ]
THAT'S WHAT SHE PROMISED US.

1034
01:40:07,367 --> 01:40:11,871
IMAGINE THE PEACE
OF LYING DOWN WITH YOUR HANDS
ACROSS YOUR CHEST.

1035
01:40:11,871 --> 01:40:13,873
YOU GO TO HELL.

1036
01:40:16,376 --> 01:40:19,379
IMAGINE HER WAITING FOR YOU
ALL THESE YEARS.

1037
01:40:19,379 --> 01:40:22,382
IMAGINE HER SLEEPING
UNDER ICE AND SNOW.

1038
01:40:22,382 --> 01:40:25,885
- WAITING.
- THE POND.

1039
01:40:26,386 --> 01:40:30,890
WOULDN'T YOU LIKE
TO BE IMMORTAL,
EVEN IF YOU MUST DIE FIRST ?

1040
01:40:30,890 --> 01:40:33,393
GOOD LORD,
SHE'S IN THE POND.

1041
01:40:33,393 --> 01:40:36,896
ALIVE.

1042
01:40:36,896 --> 01:40:38,898
STILL ALIVE.

1043
01:40:38,898 --> 01:40:41,901
SH-SHE TRICKED YOU !
YOU WON'T LIVE FOREVER.

1044
01:40:41,901 --> 01:40:44,404
OH, I'LL LIVE LONGER
THAN YOU.

1045
01:40:44,404 --> 01:40:46,906
OH, NO, YOU WON'T !

1046
01:41:04,340 --> 01:41:08,344
[ Squeaking ]

1047
01:41:14,851 --> 01:41:17,854
[ Water Running ]

1048
01:41:36,372 --> 01:41:38,875
[ Woman Laughing ]

1049
01:41:46,883 --> 01:41:48,885
[ Thud ]

1050
01:41:51,387 --> 01:41:54,891
[ Breathing Heavily ]
OH.

1051
01:42:05,902 --> 01:42:09,405
[ Wind Howling ]

1052
01:42:22,418 --> 01:42:25,421
[ Squeaks ]

1053
01:42:31,427 --> 01:42:33,930
[ Dress Rustling ]

1054
01:42:52,448 --> 01:42:53,950
[ Water Trickling ]

1055
01:42:59,455 --> 01:43:03,459
[ Stairs Creak ]

1056
01:43:04,627 --> 01:43:08,130
[ Siren Wailing ]

1057
01:43:08,130 --> 01:43:11,634
YOU'RE OUTTA YOUR SKULL.
YOU KNOW THAT, MR. HAWTHORNE ?

1058
01:43:13,636 --> 01:43:17,139
WE'VE GOT TO HURRY.
WE'VE GOT TO HELP
THE BOY.

1059
01:43:38,160 --> 01:43:41,163
[ Ice Breaking ]

1060
01:43:52,174 --> 01:43:54,677
AREN'T YOU EVEN
GOING TO SAY HELLO ?

1061
01:43:58,681 --> 01:44:00,683
OH, DON,
YOU DISAPPOINT ME.

1062
01:44:01,183 --> 01:44:03,185
[ Moans ]

1063
01:44:09,692 --> 01:44:13,696
I THOUGHT YOU'D
BE DYING TO SEE ME.

1064
01:44:13,696 --> 01:44:16,699
[ Trembling ]
Y-YOU'RE NOT HERE.

1065
01:44:16,699 --> 01:44:19,702
YOU'RE NOT HERE.

1066
01:44:19,702 --> 01:44:23,205
TALK SENSE, DON.
YOU CAN SEE ME, CAN'T YOU ?

1067
01:44:23,205 --> 01:44:25,207
YOU CAN HEAR ME.

1068
01:44:29,211 --> 01:44:32,715
- I'M HERE.
- GET AWAY FROM ME !

1069
01:44:32,715 --> 01:44:34,717
[ Laughs ]

1070
01:44:39,722 --> 01:44:41,223
FASTER !

1071
01:44:41,724 --> 01:44:44,226
POOR DON.

1072
01:44:45,227 --> 01:44:48,230
HAVEN'T YOU BEEN
LONGING FOR ME ?

1073
01:44:51,233 --> 01:44:53,235
WAITING FOR ME ?

1074
01:44:57,239 --> 01:45:01,744
- I'VE COME FOR YOU.
- YOU'RE DEAD !

1075
01:45:01,744 --> 01:45:04,246
AND YOU WILL BE TOO.

1076
01:45:04,246 --> 01:45:07,750
DEAD AND WET AND COLD.

1077
01:45:16,258 --> 01:45:19,261
DON'T YOU WANT
TO MAKE LOVE TO ME ?

1078
01:45:23,766 --> 01:45:27,269
DON'T YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT YOU'VE TOUCHED ?

1079
01:45:27,269 --> 01:45:31,774
[ Screaming ]

1080
01:45:40,282 --> 01:45:43,786
I WILL TAKE YOU PLACES
WHERE YOU'VE NEVER BEEN.

1081
01:45:51,794 --> 01:45:56,799
I WILL SHOW YOU THINGS
THAT YOU HAVE NEVER SEEN.
NO.

1082
01:46:01,804 --> 01:46:05,808
AND I WILL SEE THE LIFE
RUN OUT OF YOU.

1083
01:46:07,309 --> 01:46:09,812
[ Screaming ]

1084
01:47:43,405 --> 01:47:46,408
[ Church Bell Tolling ]

1085
01:47:57,620 --> 01:48:01,624
CLOSED-CAPTIONED BY
CAPTIONS, INC.  LOS ANGELES

